<td align="right" width="132" height="30" valign="bottom">
<p align="right">
<font SIZE="2">
<a href="0_img/TWEEDALE-Gunpowder%20&%20Saws%20(24%20January%202016).pdf" target="_blank">
<img border="0" src="../../00-000-globIncl/intNavImg/sPDF.jpg" width="24" height="24"></a></font><font style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: 700">&nbsp;
